同独闯 8 强，在 1/4 决赛中不敌日本小将张本美和。中国队无人晋级 4 强。 女双方面，由于孙颖莎退赛，中国队仅剩陈幸同 / 蒯曼一对临时组合继续征战。两人并无正式比赛搭档经历，但因王曼昱退赛，陈幸同才临时「救场」。两人一路过关斩将，在 1/4 决赛中战胜世界排名第二的申裕斌 / 田志希，晋级 4 强。13 日的半决赛中，两人接连三局惜败，以 10 比 12 、 9 比 11 、 11 比 13 不敌世界排名第 7 位的大藤沙月 / 横井咲樱，无缘当晚的决赛。后者在今年 WTT 常规挑战赛中已收获 3 冠 1 亚，实力不俗。女单、女双、女团全部无缘登顶，中国女乒 50 年来亚锦赛首次 0 冠"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3d1920978eb728e566ac7fbbf1dd9348_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "287 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/856317982"}}, "attached_info": "CkAIxZ7z9vHtm4k8EAMaCTExMTEyNTAyOCDjsq64BjAAOKkCQANyCTg1NjMxNzk4MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "4_1728900539.550193", "card_id": "Q_397229660", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 70}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "公司不提供电脑，员工自带电脑，每月补助 200，是更节约成本吗？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-004566af0513e837e389333549c50bcf_xl.jpg?source=57bbeac9"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "141 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/397229660"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4IxZ7z9vHtm4k8EAMaCDUwNTUyNzg2IPPsrfYFMAA4VEAEcgkzOTcyMjk2NjB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "5_1728900539.550436", "card_id": "Q_665746916", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count":